reviews.review_text: Maine Magic The sun shined through the back door and brightly on the band at this stellar tour closer. I saw the last three shows of this tour and each one was better than the one before it. This new to archive FOB recording sounds sweet like a lullaby to a golden time. Crank it up and I'm sure you'll agree.
